    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for this incredible project opportunity! This car is the perfect canvas for a mechanical enthusiast or someone looking for a valuable parts vehicle. While it currently requires significant repair and some TLC to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic starting point at a price that leaves plenty of room in your budget for parts and upgrades. If you love a good restoration challenge, this is the one for you!",
