    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in absolute showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or marks. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a complete, documented history available for review. Garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, it performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of a modern classic, complete with all original keys and manuals.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
